2026-05-16T05:24:19.2709537Z 22    <!--
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2710117Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2710868Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2711613Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2712634Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2713438Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2714236Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2715028Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2715843Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2716643Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2717402Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2718063Z 33    -->
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2718679Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2719692Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-16T05:24:19.2721179Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
