2026-05-16T05:24:19.3667978Z 248            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-16T05:24:19.3668798Z 249            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-16T05:24:19.3669523Z 250            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-16T05:24:19.3670262Z 251            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-16T05:24:19.3671129Z 252            finishes the activity as soon as it leaves the foreground so it
2026-05-16T05:24:19.3672175Z 253            is never re-entered with a missing extra. Library 8.x adds its
2026-05-16T05:24:19.3673008Z 254            own configChanges absorber and a v2 proxy, both of which we
